{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"628554-exam-fever","title":"Febarr Jongateh","description":"Jongateh sey jangukai suma yaye, bi ko joh yaram buu tanga  wahtu bu neka beh sunu kerr yap jahasoo.","language":"Wolof","langCode":"wo","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Isatou Fofana"],"illustrators":["Priya Kuriyan"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"AfLIA","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/628554-exam-fever"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/727674/size3/8f8c33f70a4806d41efd626c5cf14df3.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/727674/size6/8f8c33f70a4806d41efd626c5cf14df3.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673940/size6/64323183a320c4c974742f86639ad2f4.jpg","text":"nyenetty fann bala jongateh bi di jot laa suma yaye yaramam bi dolie tanga!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673941/size6/82e67f962df826cd55419659812e0aca.jpg","text":"Suma mam defal ko Wonjo buwi mu woiyal ko danka.' wayyi dole jongateh bi munuyow bai.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673942/size6/7a2196ed49e7836180b7f9582d877a9e.jpg","text":"suma 'bai mu teg morsur bu toi sey jaiyam bi","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673943/size6/551d274fec2dea20ab480480361c6d04.jpg","text":"suma 'Bai mu talii kawaram bi joko mu laika, paski....","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673944/size6/8e47726d60b6b450fcc25224f580f0c2.jpg","text":"wajal jongateh bi biss, bu neka moi yoka tanyii yarami suma yaye bu bahk,","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673945/size6/08a09ac3f40d33cccbde90ca9d3ab14a.jpg","text":"Bhaiya dom mam bu gorro bi jagal ko sey kaw . Mu wah aferi nekah sey kanam, yaa lolu du laa begu loo?''","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673946/size6/1364ed53008954bd51eed09b92ef7bec.jpg","text":"''Bul ragal laa domam bi wah, mugeh maneru lu rey loo yayam. dii wah lu ko rey loo.\nPesske.....","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673947/size6/06807af1a036281570e92526a3a14987.jpg","text":"Ken munyow sett sey du dakadorr du harrit suma yayi yaram'' bi sey dorrie tanga teh to bai.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673948/size6/9ce6c2f42bea8a942693892d9a864894.jpg","text":"watu bi jothna\nBissi jongateh bi jothna. Yaa jona werr teh degarr yaram bu tanga bi dem na, jaleh bii jeh naa.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673949/size6/176afa86807ac7171313165d488b594b.jpg","text":"Ham gaa luu hew?","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673950/size6/cd9bf868a00ecdddccd1dba07aba90df.jpg","text":"Suma yayi ama naa ndam bu mag sey jongateh bi!","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/673951/size6/d9c6a630ce185c1862b251be9f52ce04.jpg","text":"13/13","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":161}}